"snippet" : "So that the process I\/Os can be represented as BACnet data points, a simple arbitration of the I\/Os with a BACnetAnalogInput or BACnetAnalogOutput is performed in function blocks of the sample application. The ExampleAirConditioning1_using_BACnet function block and the ExampleAirConditioning1 visual...", 
