"snippet" : "The alarm classes Warning and WarningOrange   are defined in the A larm Configuration . The WarningOrange alarm class requires an additional acknowledgement. An alarm is defined by an alarm condition and an alarm class in the alarm group. The visualization user can use the buttons there to set the a...", 
