"snippet" : "In the PLC_PRG program, the ClientManagerListener function block is registered at the global ClientManager . In the SetStartVisu function, the visualization is set depending on the screen size of the client. This function is called by the StartVisualizationSet method of the ClientManagerListener . Y...", 
