"snippet" : "Using the XML Utility SL Library Product : CODESYS IIOT Libraries SL The XML Utility SL Example.project sample project shows how to use of the XML Utility SL library. The sample project contains applications with visualizations for reading and writing XML files. The individual elements are stored in...", 
