"breadcrumbs" : "CODESYS Examples \/ Examples CODESYS Application Composer \/ Example: Application Composer Examples \/ Example: SequenceEditor \/ Description ", 
"snippet" : "You can use the sequence editor to edit the module tree in the form of a graphical sequence representation. To do this, you need to define and program the steps which should be added to the program sequence later as corresponding modules. For more information, see: Mechatronics library and mse.Seque...", 
